data.description: Nestled in the heart of Fleming Island Plantation in the Johns Landing subdivision, you will find this gorgeous move in ready home!  Through the 8-foot custom doors step into the spacious foyer that opens to the family room, dining room and gourmet kitchen with California granite countertops, stainless farm sink, built-in stainless-steel appliances with vented hood and cafÃƒÂ© nook.  The family room offers 9-box coffered ceiling, recessed lighting and built-ins next to the stone fireplace. The master bedroom catches the eye with a double step tray ceiling and large bay window. The separate sinks, dual closets, and glass shower enclosure in the master bathroom are some of the many beautiful upgrades. Beautifully carpeted stairs lead to the guest suite with walk-in closet and full bath. Large 3 car garage is a bonus for working & playing at home. Don't miss this home and all the amenities included with it! Many more upgrades are listed under the documents tab!
